# Exclude Python bytecode caches from Databricks Apps deploys.
# Stale __pycache__/*.pyc would otherwise be uploaded alongside app.py
# and Python may load the (older) bytecode instead of the source — code
# changes appear not to take effect until the cache is purged.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Local editor / OS noise that has no place in the deployed app.
.DS_Store
*.swp
.vscode/
.idea/
